InPlaceElementStructure Properties

Requires: VI Scripting

Inherits from Node»Structure. View the class hierarchy.

PropertyDescription
DecomposerList[]Returns an array of references to any of the following border nodes on the In Place Element structure: Array Index Elements, Array Split Subarrays, Unbundle Elements, Waveform Unbundle Elements, Variant To Element, In Place In Element, Data Value Reference Read Element. Details
